creator: Panda Rolling
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy sudoku puzzle with this simple clean sudoku app.

Features

• clean interfaces, intuitive interactions.
• play both classic and jigsaw sudoku with four difficulty levels.
• never get interrupted by ads when playing.
• support light/dark mode, with multiple different color themes to choose from.
• free-fill by choosing a number first or fill specific square by choosing a square first.
• take notes like you did on paper.
• erase by double tap.
• pick up right where you left off, game progress autosaved
• made too much mistakes? just rollback with checkpoints.
